<h1>Book Swap Request from <%= @requester.name %></h1>

<p>Hi <%= @requestee.name %>,</p>

<p><strong><%= @requester.name %></strong> has requested a book swap with you for the following listing:</p>

<div style="margin: 20px 0; padding: 15px; background-color: #f5f5f5; border-left: 4px solid #007bff;">
  <h3><%= @listing.title %></h3>
  <p><strong>Author:</strong> <%= @listing.author_name %></p>
  <% if @listing.description %>
    <p><strong>Description:</strong> <%= @listing.description %></p>
  <% end %>
</div>

<p>Log in to your account to view the full details and respond to this request.</p>

<p>Best regards,<br/>
The Kitab Sata Pata Team</p>
